lead_paragraph: Italy coach Antonio Conte will field a five-man midfield in a trademark 3-5-2 formation for his team's last-16 clash against champions Spain at Euro 2016 on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Italy Field Five-Man Midfield Against Unchanged Spain
